Metadata: New lamellarin alkaloids from an unidentified ascidian from the Arabian Sea

An unidentified ascidian from the Arabian Sea contained nine new alkaloids of the lamellarin class together with lamellarin N. The structures of the 20-sulfate derivates of lamellarins T, U, V, and Y and lamellarins T-X were identified by interpretation of spectroscopic data. This is the first report of lamellarin sulfates.
